
Overview
--------
pokemon is a structure based variance component test for studying rare variants

Dependencies
------------
python > 3.6
fastlmm
pandas

Installation
------------
git clone 

Example:
-----------------------
python pokemon.py --gene_name ERBB3 --genotype test.vcf --cov_file test.cov --cov_list APOE4_dose,APOE2_dose --reference snp_coords.tab
